            <scopecontent id="aspace_61f257308b4f484cf1b7a9202ae7b740">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Original engraved print by Amos Doolittle (New Haven, Conn.), featuring a Head-and-shoulders portrait of George Washington, "President of the United States of America. The protector of his country, and the supporter of the rights of mankind." Inter-looped circle of the Seal of the United States and 13 state seals encompass the portrait.</p>
            </scopecontent>
